				sdlpathfinder

		sdlpathfinder is a visual grid-based path finder

This is mainly a project for me to learn SDL and C. If you have any
recommendations on how I could improve, please send a pull request.

CONTROLS:

      s        Step the pathfinder once

      q        Quit the application

BUILD SYSTEM:

      This project uses GNU Autotools. To generate the configure script, run
      `autoreconf -i`. You can then follow the instructions in INSTALL.
